answers.answer: I would check with your dr. Just to make sure everything's ok. It might be nothing but better safe than sry.

Don't worry, I had the same problem from 13 weeks till 23 weeks it was constant headaches. I was told to use icy hot and a heating pad on my neck. It worked for a while, then wore off. My OB prescribed me something for my headaches and it worked wonders. Tylenol just wouldn't work. Talk to your OB and let them know.
